channel.title: Looking for a few Java scriptors to help me make a leet private server!
channel.description: hey guys. well i have started a private server and all. I tried two different sources (cheezescape and nixscape) but i am having problems with both. i got the actual servers runnin but i am not so good with java so if there is any1 or two ppl to help me we can all make a private server that p00ns. how we can do that is i can host it, and we'll all have the same files at the same time and we will be sharing the scripts through msn. any edits and such we will all be talkin about. than the scripts i'll edit and we can all talk on msn if i am gettin any errors and such. we'll also all be admins and high lvls lolz. so if there is any1 good with java scriptin at all plz post here. also we will have to discuss what you think the best source is since i am disappointed with both nixscape and cheezescape. ty

item.title: Looking for a few Java scriptors to help me make a leet private server!
item.dc:creator: @moparisthebest Moparisthebest
item.description:
@moparisthebest wrote:

[quote=“Vipsta, post:4, topic:5194”][quote author=x3mvess link=topic=6805.msg69744#msg69744 date=1153160124]
lolz dude i am not paying. i just want us all to combine our brains and make a leet server.
[/quote]

No one is going to want to work on your ‘leet’ server, especially when projects like HybridScape are far more along.[/quote]

Hybridscape is the way to go, there is a team of developers on it, and you can check out the latest source from the svn at any moment in time, check it out at hybriscape.sourceforge.net
